1. *Nebu* je tako lepo vreme, da ćemo svi izaći napolje. (It's such a nice weather, that we will all go outside.)

2. Ovi oblaci su se tako brzo pojavili, da smo očekivali da *nebu* padne kiša. (These clouds appeared so fast, that we were expecting it to rain.)

3. Uvek kada me obuzme tuga, zašto se *nebi* okrenula bolja strana? (Whenever I feel sad, why can't the better side turn around?)

4. Njegov osmeh je bio tako blistav, da je osvetlio *nebo*. (His smile was so bright, that it lit up the sky.)

5. Ona je uvek bila nebeski čovek, zbog njenog prevelikog srca. (*Nebu* je uvek bila blizu.) (She was always an angelic person, due to her big heart. The sky was always close to her.)